fields.name: ARGENTINA HOME SHIRT 2022/23
fields.description: Designed in the iconic Argentina home colours, this jersey features alternating sky blue and white vertical stripes. On the front of the shirt the stripes are equal in size, there are thinner stripes down running down the centre back creating a unique look. Black side seam and rear hem tape, alongside black Adidas shoulder stripes and front logo stand out against the blue and white shirt. There is also a fully embroidered Argentina badge on the front.

If your child is a junior goalkeeper, this shirt is a must-have addition to their kit bag. Lightweight, breathable polyester with integrated dryCELL sweat management actively wicks away moisture keeping your child cool and confident.

fields.name: CHELSEA HOME MATCH SHIRT 2022/23
fields.description:
Here we have the authentic home shirt for Chelsea as worn by the players this season. Dispatched from Nike and delivered directly to our warehouse, our supply of this Chelsea Home Match Shirt 2022/23 is 100% official. Complete with Nikeâ€™s patch of authenticity, get your hands on this player shirt in small to xx-large adults while stocks last!

For 2022/23 the bold blue base colour synonymous with Chelsea is background to white and turquoise accents to create a stylish jersey for the new season. The main feature of this shirt Is the neckline which features a buttoned fastening and a white collar with turquoise lion graphic. Adorned to the front of the chest is the Nike Swoosh in white with the Chelsea crest sitting proudly on the left. Sponsors can also be seen in the centre of the chest and on the left sleeve.

On the front of the shirt is a FC Bayern badge, Adidas, and sponsor logos. fields.name: BARCELONA HOME SHIRT 2022/23
fields.description: Styled for the 22/23 football season, this edition of the Barca home shirt is navy with navy, blue, and red vertical stripes, the sleeves, and neckline are plain. There is a Barcelona badge on the left of the chest and the iconic Nike logo opposite; both are fully embroidered for a premium finish. In the centre of the jersey is a heat-applied Spotify logo, and there is printed Spanish flag detail on the back of the jersey below the collar.

fields.name: MANCHESTER CITY KIDS GREEN GOALKEEPER SHIRT 2023/24
fields.description: Styled in an iconic goalkeeper colour, this edition of the Man City goalie jersey is primarily two-tone green making it a great choice for junior supporters. The front of the shirt accented with a chevron graphic. There are yellow inserts on both sides featuring a green pattern. On the front of the shirt is a Man City badge and Puma logo that are both embroidered, alongside a heat-applied sponsor logo.

fields.name: BRAZIL AWAY SHIRT 2022/23
fields.description: Featuring a bold new design for 2022, this edition of the Brazil away jersey is bright blue in colour. There is a patterned sleeve that includes a transitional green to blue colour gradient. Green ribbed sleeve cuffs are accented with thinner yellow hoops. On the front of the shirt is a Brazil badge on the left that is flanked by 5 World Cup winner stars and a â€˜Brasilâ€™ text logo. A green Nike Swoosh sits opposite. These logos are embroidered for a premium finish. Completing the design is a printed Brazil logo on the back collar.

fields.name: GERMANY AUTHENTIC AWAY SHIRT 2022/23
fields.description: Black with a burgundy graphic, and gold coloured detail, this edition of the Germany away jersey oozes pride in the 4-time World Cup winning team. Burgundy binding on the side seams, and around the dropped rear hem adds a premium touch. Gold coloured Adidas stripes adorn the shoulders. On the front there is an Adidas Badge of Sport and Germany badge; both embossed for a lightweight finish.

fields.name: JUVENTUS AUTHENTIC HOME SHIRT 2023/24

Supplied directly by Adidas, you are guaranteed to receive an official Juventus authentic home shirt 2023/24 when you shop at Soccer Box. Order online to secure yours and get ready to highlight your allegiance to the team on match days and every day.

fields.name: MANCHESTER CITY AUTHENTIC HOME SHIRT 2023/24

On the front of the jersey is a vertical stripe pattern made up of tonal blue horizontal stripes that emulate features of the stadium. The sleeves and back are plain blue, a white collar and logos stand out perfectly. There is a Manchester City badge on the front of the top, alongside a Puma CAT logo and sponsorship logo.
